      • getPolicyChecksum

        @Deprecated(value="The new exposure menu is constructed lazily in ClaimCenter 5.0 (and later) so this checksum should no longer be used")
public static java.lang.Object getPolicyChecksum(Claim claim)
        Deprecated. The new exposure menu is constructed lazily in ClaimCenter 5.0 (and later) so this checksum should no longer be used
        Returns a checksum for a policy's coverages. If this checksum changes then the exposure menu needs to be rebuild to take account of the changed coverages.
        Parameters:
        claim - the claim to get the policy checksum for
        Returns:
        checksum for the policy's coverages. The only thing you need to know about this checksum is that you can compare it with previous checksums to see if it is equal; no other methods need to be exposed
